# PROJECT RULES

## NAMING

Product/marketing name: **AyNesil** (UI display text, landing page,
README title, marketing copy only).

Technical/code identifier: **Aynesil** (PascalCase, no internal
capitalization) — use consistently for:

- Solution name: Aynesil.sln
- Project namespaces: Aynesil.Domain, Aynesil.Application,
  Aynesil.Infrastructure, Aynesil.Api, Aynesil.Shared, Aynesil.Tests
- Database name: aynesil (lowercase)
- Docker container/service names: aynesil-api, aynesil-db, aynesil-redis
- Environment variable prefixes: AYNESIL_
- Frontend package name: aynesil-web

Never use "AyNesil" (mixed case) in code, namespaces, file paths,
database identifiers, or config keys.

"Akran Hareket" is a tenant/customer name (a row in
`core.corporation`), not the platform name — never used in code,
namespaces, or technical identifiers.

---

